name: 2021.10(1) WHITEDUCKSTICKERS
description:
This October 2021 White Duck Sticker was designed by Lindsi Werner. The Grim Reaper Duck is one of four designs for October, 2021.

Each month White Duck Espresso works with a local artist to re-imagine the duck in their style. They are printed as physical stickers in one-off limited print runs and sold at White Duck Espresso drive-thru espresso stands until they're sold out.

GIFs are created from each sticker design, and only 5 are minted of each month's design(s).
